-- Mets Invite Alderson, Byrnes for Second-Round General Manager Interviews
-- B y   M i c h a e l   S i l l u p
-- 2010-10-22T19:34:07Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-22/mets-invite-alderson-byrnes-for-second-round-general-manager-interviews.html
The New York Mets are inviting  Sandy Alderson  and  Josh Byrnes  back for a second round of interviews
for the Major League Baseball team’s vacant general manager
position, the team said in a statement.  Alderson formerly was the Oakland Athletics’ general
manager. Byrnes was the Arizona Diamondbacks’ general manager
from 2005 until being fired in July.  To contact the reporter on this story:
 Michael Sillup  in New York at 
 msillup@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
